<TEXT>
<P>
The Bendix Automotive Systems Group of Allied-Signal Inc. has announced plans 
to phase out some vehicle disc brake operations at its St. Joseph, Mich., 
complex and build a facility in Roanoke, VA. 
</P>
<P>
