tug-of-war between prosecutors in California and in Tahiti, where she has been 
charged with complicity in Drollet's death. Drollet's father, Jacques, said 
today that he was told the young woman, who gave birth to Drollet's child in 
June, was out of her coma. He said he believed her act was the suicide attempt 
